{"tid":516850,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我想知我男朋友咁做係諗緊咩？","createTime":"2018-01-01T18:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T02:14:08.000Z","uid":143453,"like":3,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"267ea52e471e1957a27c8e41a110570ac0ce9611","tid":516850,"uid":143453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:17:20.000Z","msg":"我男朋友同我一齊一年半到<br />\n佢就成日到緊急關頭跳大制<br />\n個大制個名叫反社會人格?<br />\n<br />\n同左我一齊咁耐 第一次見家長<br />\n上黎見到我呀媽唔叫 細佬都冇應<br />\n連我示意佢 都係低頭繼續<br />\n<br />\n第二次上黎 咁岩老豆係度<br />\n我又拔又揑都係冇叫到叔叔<br />\n超尷尬<br />\n<br />\n最後尋日1月1 同朋友食飯<br />\n我入到餐廳門口 坐底望返轉頭<br />\n佢一支箭咁跑走左<br />\n<br />\n但我認識嘅佢唔係咁樣<br />\n佢好開朗 好多朋友<br />\n人好聰明又考順<br />\n佢上朋友屋企都會叫人<br />\n雖然笨拙 但感覺到佢真心對你"},{"pid":"d69b5022d4a5795f50df5bbd381b41c2bfdf3a37","tid":516850,"uid":143453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:17:55.000Z","msg":"我真係唔明 佢到底諗緊咩野"},{"pid":"4784bbb3be1447857cbb1bea4964c533db5d4438","tid":516850,"uid":4826,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:18:44.000Z","msg":"佢想飛左你"},{"pid":"89211d20e2c100555678a572b93b44be7dd2c5b6","tid":516850,"uid":32324,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:19:07.000Z","msg":"驚？緊張？無傾過？佢本身有無預計個日要見人先"},{"pid":"eed70c5d6d2ea8b4455ae52364cbf88350dec7b2","tid":516850,"uid":39215,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:20:12.000Z","msg":"低能仔"},{"pid":"9317931735ba84f7d0c2deacabb53f6fdd607eea","tid":516850,"uid":96877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:20:21.000Z","msg":"俾鬼搞係咁"},{"pid":"491bf0cb0a91c72db142ece7960b49201945d8f0","tid":516850,"uid":143453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89211d20e2c100555678a572b93b44be7dd2c5b6","tid":516850,"uid":32324,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:19:07.000Z","msg":"驚？緊張？無傾過？佢本身有無預計個日要見人先"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:20:23.000Z","msg":"有同佢講過 <br />\n佢唔係唔識禮貌<br />\n佢仲好